quran[8{c,v,t}:
35,4,"ab agar ( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) yeh log tumhe jutlatay hain ( to yeh koi nai baat nahi ), tum se pehlay bhi bohat se rasooljhutla-ay ja chuke hain, aur saaray mamlaat aakhir kaar Allah hi ki taraf rujoo honay walay hain"
35,5,"logo, Allah ka wada yaqeenan barhaq hai, lehaza duniya ki zindagi tumhe dhokay mein nah daaley aur nah woh bara dhokay baz tumhe Allah ke baray mein dhoka dainay paye"
35,6,Dur haqeeqat shetan tumhara dushman hai is liye tum bhi usay apna dushman hi samjhoo woh to apne pairwoon ko apni raah par is liye bulaa raha hai ke woh dozakhyon mein shaamil ho jayen
35,7,jo log kufar karen ge unn ke liye sakht azaab hai aur jo imaan layein ge aur naik amal karen ge unn ke liye mughfirat aur bara ajar hai
35,8,( bhala kuch thikana hai uss shakhs ki gumraahi ka ) jis ke liye uss ka bura amal khushnuma bana diya gaya ho aur woh ussay acha samajh raha ho? haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah jisay chahta hai gumraahi mein daal deta hai aur jisay chahta hai raah raast dikha deta hai pas ( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) khuwa makhuwa tumhari jaan un logon ki khatir gham o afsos mein nah ghulay jo kuch yeh kar rahay hain Allah uss ko khoob jaanta hai
35,9,"woh Allah hi to hai jo hawaon ko bhejta hai, phir woh baadal athati hain, phir hum usay aik ujaar ilaqay ki taraf le jatay hain aur isi zameen ko jِla uthatay hain jo meri pari thi marey hue insanon ka jee uthna bhi isi terhan hoga"
35,10,"jo koi izzat chahta ho ussay maloom hona chahiye ke izzat saari ki saari Allah ki hai uss ke haan jo cheez oopar chadhti hai woh sirf pakeeza qoul hai, aur amal Saleh is ko oopar chadata hai rahay woh log jo behooda chaal bazyan karte hain, unn ke liye sakht azaab hai aur unn ka makr khud hi ghaarat honay wala hai"
35,11,"Allah ne tum ko matti se peda kya, phir nutfa se, phir tumahray jore bana diye ( yani mard aur aurat ) koi aurat haamla nahi hoti aur nah bacha janati hai magar yeh sab kuch Allah ke ilm mein hota hai koi Umar panay wala Umar nahi paata aur nah kisi ki Umar mein kuch kami hoti hai magar yeh sab kuch aik kitaab mein likha hota hai Allah ke liye yeh bohat aasaan kaam hai"
